    <FileVersion>1.14.72.0</FileVersion>
    <InformationalVersion>1.14.72 (SIM Boxes report: empty-BoxNo fallback joins whboxitems.BoxNo = LPMSIM_Output.PalletNo so lone-pallet entries get their correct PalletType / GIN columns; WH Stock Position: add LPM Eligible + NonLPM Eligible columns + per-column hover tooltips showing each criterion)</InformationalVersion>
